<br />\n樓主你嗰句邊算氹 分分鍾更嬲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果佢係唔開心多過嬲<br />\n就死撚緊，佢會覺得你唔在乎佢，<br />\n佢唔開心都唔關心佢 唔氹佢<br />\n<br />\n如果佢係嬲爆<br />\n應該會畀佢不停罵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeeb2289d46ef1026e43a570e1ec421ccde4e7fd","tid":276214,"uid":119458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T02:29:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你要知佢嬲你啲咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n每次都問佢知唔知我嬲咩/ 做錯咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"490efa5b7f69e555eb79222a62e67aab52d2b350","tid":276214,"uid":85243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T02:31:01.000Z","msg":"你覺得我未嬲完又唔哄我?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96c630eb25b17db3f515e5459d7ab8ba40b9f483","tid":276214,"uid":50513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T02:31:21.000Z","msg":"咁講唔嬲都變嬲啦<br />\n<br />\n比我會問<br />\n係咪有啲咩唔開心呀？"},{"pid":"61769be775a8b4d40959b6ee589ef7622277f9b5","tid":276214,"uid":16168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T02:32:24.000Z","msg":"Send個笑話過去仲好啦"},{"pid":"eb01be003de8a206d73e48e2d07afed86a11bfe4","tid":276214,"uid":20696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T03:29:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Send個笑話過去仲好啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nAgger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果真嬲就認真傾下，唔理佢佢就覺得你唔緊佢，唔知錯喺邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔肯定嬲唔嬲/件事其實唔嚴重，女仔多數自己嬲一陣就冷靜返少少但又唔知點落台好。<br />\n你問佢嬲完未，有時佢可能想扮無野，你咁問佢又覺得你話佢小器/唔耐煩，同時令佢諗返起件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n扮下低能仔嗲兩句，若無其事講野氹下佢開心可能就無野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}